420
00:33:48,646 --> 00:33:50,766
Don't pay too much attention to those words.

421
00:33:51,726 --> 00:33:53,526
Don't lose your confidence.

422
00:33:54,622 --> 00:33:55,966
Believe in yourself

423
00:33:57,286 --> 00:33:58,606
