425
00:35:01,613 --> 00:35:04,246
Gigi...

426
00:35:09,846 --> 00:35:11,926
Gigi...

427
00:35:15,086 --> 00:35:16,206
Aum.

428
00:35:17,646 --> 00:35:18,835
